1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 20=

11
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:01,520
Once I'm done with you,

12
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:02,880
I'll send you back.

13
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:04,400
Then you can

14
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:07,359
reunite with him underground.

15
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:08,920
Don't touch me!

16
00:01:13,719 --> 00:01:14,519
Who are you?

17
00:01:17,359 --> 00:01:18,719
Guards!

18
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,760
Who the heck are you?

19
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:29,040
S-S-Senior.

20
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:32,319
I told you to bring her to me.

21
00:01:32,719 --> 00:01:34,120
What's taking so long?

22
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:35,840
Senior.

23
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:37,480
I-I think

24
00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:39,519
she and Su Wubing are going
to die anyway,

25
00:01:39,879 --> 00:01:41,159
so it'd be a waste not to...

26
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:48,239
How dare you ruin my plan.

27
00:01:50,359 --> 00:01:51,159
Please.

28
00:01:53,719 --> 00:01:54,439
No...

29
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,840
Who are you?

30
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:06,040
With you, I can get his soul.

31
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,000
(I failed to beat the Heavenly Dao)

32
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:54,199
(because the sword wasn't fully forged.)

33
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:58,319
(With the spirit stone,
everything will be easy now.)

34
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,319
Sword, come!

35
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:58,159
Congratulations on reaching
the Heavenly God Realm.

36
00:03:58,439 --> 00:04:00,639
With the sword as well,

37
00:04:01,319 --> 00:04:05,560
we might just change the world.

38
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,680
I reached the Heavenly God realm

39
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,280
for Ningxue.

40
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,159
No time to waste.

41
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:11,120
Let's...

42
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:30,360
Break!

43
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:38,959
I set up a barrier here.

44
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:41,360
It couldn't be broken so easily.

45
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,079
Who is this?

46
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,240
Hello?

47
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,160
Su Wubing, Ningxue...

48
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,839
My Lord, look!

49
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,160
It's you.

50
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:04,240
Long time no see.

51
00:05:04,759 --> 00:05:06,600
I told you at the teahouse.

52
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:10,680
the day I come out, I'll take your soul.

53
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,399
If you want to save Lin Ningxue,

54
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:16,439
come to the rooftop
of Gu Group tomorrow.

55
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,360
Remember,

56
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:19,680
come alone.

57
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:23,199
Otherwise,
I'll tear her soul apart first.

58
00:05:23,199 --> 00:05:23,560
You!

59
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,360
My Lord.

60
00:05:26,079 --> 00:05:27,399
Who is that?

61
00:05:30,439 --> 00:05:31,759
A descendant of the Demon Clan.

62
00:05:32,519 --> 00:05:33,319
What?

63
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:37,480
After ten thousand years,
the demons still won't quit.

64
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,600
I'll go with you.

65
00:05:40,319 --> 00:05:41,600
You'll need backup.

66
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:42,560
No.

67
00:05:43,279 --> 00:05:44,399
I have to go alone.

68
00:05:44,839 --> 00:05:46,319
Ningxue is in his hands.

69
00:05:47,319 --> 00:05:49,600
I need to do as he said.

70
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,360
Su Wubing.

71
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,680
You actually came alone.

72
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,839
Where's Ningxue?

73
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,319
I thought you were so capable.

74
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,079
Find her yourself.

75
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:12,920
Let Ningxue go

76
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,079
and I might spare you.

77
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,279
Even if you colluded
with the Ancient God Sect,

78
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,199
I could let that slide too.

79
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:22,480
You think you're in a position
to bargain with me?

80
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:23,720
You made me kneel last time.

81
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:24,920
We're not done with that.

82
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,519
Kneel. Now.

83
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,839
If you make me happy,

84
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:31,240
maybe I'll let you see her
one last time.

85
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:38,800
Senior.

86
00:06:42,319 --> 00:06:43,360
Immortal King,

87
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,000
you never thought

88
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,120
you'd be trapped
in a mortal body again, did you?

89
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,000
Let Ningxue go.

90
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:51,920
Fine.

91
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:54,120
Then destroy your own spiritual core

92
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,920
and trade your soul.

93
00:06:57,920 --> 00:07:00,399
This is between us.
Don't drag her into it.

94
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:05,399
You never change.

95
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:08,040
She's still your weakness.

96
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,120
Ten thousand years ago,

97
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:12,399
you defied the Heavenly Dao

98
00:07:12,399 --> 00:07:13,920
just to break her curse.

99
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:16,120
You gave your life

100
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:17,720
and spent ten thousand years alone.

101
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:21,519
Yet her curse still remains.

102
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:25,240
Now you're pushing your limits again,

103
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:27,120
still trying to save her.

104
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,399
What...

105
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,879
How dare you!

106
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,639
Tianmiao!

107
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,639
That all you got, old man?

108
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:56,600
Tianmiao, you can't beat him.

109
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,279
My Lord.

110
00:07:58,040 --> 00:08:01,360
Back when the Heavenly Dao descended,
I couldn't help you.

111
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:02,879
This time,

112
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,680
I will stand with you.

113
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,000
How touching.

114
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,000
Grandpa!

115
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:15,279
How did you get hurt so badly?

116
00:08:20,759 --> 00:08:22,759
Senior, they're in the way.

117
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:24,040
Why not just wipe them all out?

118
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,399
Su Wubing,

119
00:08:27,079 --> 00:08:29,879
I only came for you.

120
00:08:30,279 --> 00:08:32,679
But if you let them
throw their lives away,

121
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:35,279
don't blame me.

122
00:08:35,879 --> 00:08:37,000
Big talk.

123
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:38,679
You're asking for it.

124
00:09:04,478 --> 00:09:08,581
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

125
00:09:08,581 --> 00:09:13,301
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

126
00:09:13,301 --> 00:09:18,181
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

127
00:09:18,181 --> 00:09:23,301
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

128
00:09:23,301 --> 00:09:27,701
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

129
00:09:27,701 --> 00:09:32,381
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

130
00:09:32,381 --> 00:09:37,781
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

131
00:09:37,781 --> 00:09:44,175
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

